      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, meticulously maintained for the purist. This example features the S54B32 high-revving inline-six, factory-rated at 333 hp, paired with a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical state is superlative: preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul have been completed. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with no bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is exceptional and the interior remains free of typical bolster wear or trim delamination. A true turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
